### Root cause
Production is running a Phase 1-2 build. Phase 3-4 features (FEAT-049 and friends) only exist on `ralph/init-stride` — not merged to `main`, not deployed. The `[tabId]` dynamic route catches all unrecognized paths and renders the canvas fallback. A production deploy of the branch is required before these checks can pass.
